1x1 Aspect Ratio, Two-Line Captions with Icons

```js
const image = require("./16-9.jpg");
const tiles = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5];

<GridList aspectRatio="1x1" twoLineCaption iconAlign="start">
  <GridListTiles>
    {tiles.map(id => (
      <GridTile key={id}>
        <GridTilePrimary>
          <GridTilePrimaryContent src={image} />
        </GridTilePrimary>
        <GridTileSecondary>
          <GridTileIcon>star_border</GridTileIcon>
          <GridTileTitle>Title</GridTileTitle>
          <GridTileSupportText>Secondary text</GridTileSupportText>
        </GridTileSecondary>
      </GridTile>
    ))}
  </GridListTiles>
</GridList>;
```

16x9 Aspect Ratio, 1px gutter, Single-Line Caption at Top

```js
const image = require("./16-9.jpg");
const tiles = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5];

<GridList aspectRatio="16x9" tileGutter1 headerCaption>
  <GridListTiles>
    {tiles.map(id => (
      <GridTile key={id}>
        <GridTilePrimary>
          <GridTilePrimaryContent src={image} />
        </GridTilePrimary>
        <GridTileSecondary>
          <GridTileTitle>Title</GridTileTitle>
        </GridTileSecondary>
      </GridTile>
    ))}
  </GridListTiles>
</GridList>;
```
